"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-07-hugo-hay-responds-george-mills-bust-up-5000m-olympic-heat-21377504\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Hugo Hay says he 'understands' the anger from George Mills after their bust-up at the end of the 5000m Olympic qualifier on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 134, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 103, \"end\": 120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_American_Boxing_Olympic_Qualification_Tournament\", \"score\": 0.8000129252602769, \"rank\": 0.24458476696722445, \"text\": \"Olympic qualifier\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_American_Boxing_Olympic_Qualification_Tournament\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_American_Boxing_Olympic_Qualification_Tournament\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mills angrily confronted Hay over the finish lineas a collision with his French rival caused him to fall on the final street of the first 5000m heat at the Stade de France.\", \"from\": 136, \"to\": 308, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 209, \"end\": 215, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6867226026409503, \"rank\": 0.28178040302037227, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 292, \"end\": 307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Team GB runner, who is the son of former England andLeeds Uniteddefender Danny Mills, also took three athletes down with him after unsuccessfully jostling for position with Hay.\", \"from\": 310, \"to\": 491, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 355, \"end\": 362, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9479092637415283, \"rank\": 0.04328387743859475, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 387, \"end\": 398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Mills\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.630294041112694e-16, \"text\": \"Danny Mills\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Mills\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Mills\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following an appeal, Mills has now advanced to Saturday's final following a review by the video referee.\", \"from\": 493, \"to\": 597, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But Hay, who will also be in the final, maintains his innocence and claims he was unaware of the contact with Mills during the closing stages of the race.\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 753, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I do not know what happened.\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 784, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not feel anything,' said Hay.\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 820, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I was surprised that George came to see me after the race, because I did not feel anything, well, no more than usual.\", \"from\": 822, \"to\": 940, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It pushed in the last 400m, it was really a massacre.\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 996, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I turned around, there was no one left.\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1036, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was incredible.\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1055, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have no idea what's going to happen, it scares me.\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1108, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'For me, it happened clearly.\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1139, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's what I said to George.\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1169, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If I am guilty, sorry, but I think I was pushed.\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1218, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not think I did anything wrong, but it scares me a little bit.\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1286, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I hope it works out and that I can get into the final.\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1343, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If the protest ever goes through and I am eliminated, of course, it will hurt but I know that I had the level to qualify and that I have never been so strong.\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1502, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For me, I am qualified, that is the most important thing.'\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1561, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hay also reiterated that he would apologise to Mills if he felt the footage proved he was in the wrong over the collision.\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1685, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'We are at very high speeds, so of course, the slightest contact throws you off balance,' Hay said.\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1786, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I was pushed two years ago and I was really angry after the line.\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 1854, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's what I told the others, I understand George's reaction, of course.\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1928, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is the adrenaline, the disappointment.\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 1973, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was very angry, he said a few sweet words to me and that it was because of me that they had fallen.\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 2076, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'He told me: 'No, I do not care what you say'.\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2124, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I told him it was normal for him to react like that.\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2177, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I told him I understood and that we would discuss it afterwards.\", \"from\": 2178, \"to\": 2242, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And that I would apologise if I am guilty, but I do not have that impression.'\", \"from\": 2243, \"to\": 2321, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When shown the footage of the incident after the race, Hay said: 'Oh yes, I am being pushed!\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2415, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Oh lalala!\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 2426, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No, for me George is coming at me.'\", \"from\": 2427, \"to\": 2462, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A furious Mills was asked by French media for his verdict and said: 'You know very well what happened.'\", \"from\": 2464, \"to\": 2567, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2493, \"end\": 2499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6867226026409503, \"rank\": 0.28178040302037227, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2617, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 2619, \"to\": 2689, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Tony Hawk responds to calls to make stunning Olympics comeback  ArrowMORE:Why is there a motorbike on the track cycling at the Olympics?\", \"from\": 2691, \"to\": 2837, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Olympic athlete 'making more from OnlyFans than rowing' thanks to 'artistic nudes'  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 2839, \"to\": 3043, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2883, \"end\": 2891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OnlyFans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"OnlyFans\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OnlyFans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OnlyFans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know which team you support.Close  This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 3045, \"to\": 3176, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your information will be used in line with ourPrivacy Policy  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 3177, \"to\": 3349, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3239, \"end\": 3245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punchy,_Somme\", \"score\": 0.6784377202962604, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Punchy\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punchy,_Somme\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punchy,_Somme\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know which team you support.Close  This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 3351, \"to\": 3482, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your information will be used in line with ourPrivacy Policy\", \"from\": 3483, \"to\": 3543, \"entities\": []}]}"